    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a masterclass in mechanical preservation. This unit features a blueprint-balanced rotating assembly that delivers surgical throttle response and a perfectly linear power band. The chassis has been optimized for maximum torsional rigidity, utilizing high-durometer bushings and dampers that have been dial-indicated for absolute symmetry. Every gear change is a tactile event, with zero synchro drag and a short-throw gate that feels factory-tight. We\u2019ve maintained a clinical environment for the engine bay, ensuring the stoichiometric ratio remains perfect and the compression profile is within nominal factory tolerances across all cylinders. This is a high-fidelity performance machine for those who demand zero-tolerance maintenance standards.",
      "price": 47850.0,
